px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 0.75em;padding:5px 10px;background:#f0f4f8;border-left:3px solid #7b9fc4;border-radius:3px;font-size:0.82em;color:#444;line-height:1.8;\">⚠️ <strong>13</strong> · 📝 Q:13 · 🎯 R:13</p>\n<a href=\"https://boingboing.net/2026/06/19/the-man-who-built-the-spaceships-for-2001-alien-and-empire-has-died.html\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"The man who built the spaceships for 2001, Alien, and Empire has died\"><img alt=\"credit: hafizi / Shutterstock.com\" class=\"webfeedsFeaturedVisual wp-post-image\" height=\"512\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/clones-e1745246791292.jpg?fit=768%2C512&amp;quality=60&amp;ssl=1\" style=\"display: block; margin: auto; margin-bottom: 5px;\" width=\"768\" /></a><p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Science fiction aficionados and fans of practical effects will want to pour one out today: Brian Johnson, a man responsible for building some of the most iconic sci-fi craft in movies and television history, has <a href=\"https://www.jedinews.com/film-music-tv/articles/academy-award-winning-special-effects-pioneer-brian-johnson-has-passed-away/\">died at the age of 87</a>. &#8212; <a class=\"read-more\" href=\"https://boingboing.net/2026/06/19/the-man-who-built-the-spaceships-for-2001-alien-and-empire-has-died.html\">Read the rest </a></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://boingboing.net/2026/06/19/the-man-who-built-the-spaceships-for-2001-alien-and-empire-has-died.html\">The man who built the spaceships for 2001, Alien, and Empire has died</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://boingboing.net\">Boing Boing</a>.</p>",
